data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch home located in the vibrant Mar Lee neighborhood of Denver. Ideal for those who need ample space for vehicles and hobbies, this property features an oversized 2-car garage, additional parking for an RV, and extra room for all your toys—all without the restrictions of an HOA! As you step through the front door, you're greeted by inviting warm colors and a comfortable atmosphere, with hardwood floors spreading across the main level. The layout includes a cozy family room, a practical kitchen, a dining area perfect for mealtime gatherings, and three well-appointed bedrooms accompanied by a full bath. This home is perfect for entertaining; the layout flows effortlessly out to a spacious covered back patio where you can enjoy BBQs and outdoor gatherings no matter the weather. The patio overlooks a peaceful backyard, providing a great space for relaxation and leisure. The versatility of this home extends to the fully finished basement, which adds significant extra living space. Here, you'll find an additional non-conforming bedroom, a bathroom, flexible space for any number of activities, and a dedicated laundry room. This lower level is perfect for guests, a home office, or simply as extra space to spread out and enjoy. Located in a friendly community with easy access to local amenities, this home combines comfort and convenience in a package that's hard to beat. Whether you’re hosting friends on the patio, tinkering in the oversized garage, or enjoying the local scene, this Mar Lee ranch home offers a unique blend of style, space, and functionality.
